Category:Unidentified Jedi of the New Jedi Order

nodes.text: A female Kitonak was trained as a Jedi in the New Jedi Order. During the Swarm War this individual was training to become a Jedi at the Ossus Academy. When Chiss Aristocra Chaf'orm'bintrano visited the academy, the apprentice leapt over the Aristocra in order to demonstrate her Force abilities.
